  "title": "Forklift Operator",
  "description": "<p>Job Description:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Store cargo in the designated/correct area according to the port</li>\n  <li>Do housekeeping and maximize usage of space and space planning</li>\n  <li>Retrieve and ensure the correct cargo for storing/stuffing according to the number stickers</li>\n  <li>Stack cargo in safe and stable manner</li>\n  <li>Serve consignees in order of queue</li>\n  <li>Retrieve correct cargo and load onto the vehicle for consignee</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Job Requirement:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 2-3 Years of working experience in operating and driving the forklift</li>\n  <li>An Independent and self-starter with strong personal drive to initiate and implement</li>\n  <li>Able to handle work pressure, highly motivated and self-driven</li>\n  <li>Good and Dynamic team player with good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Possess a valid forklift license will be an advantage</li>\n</ul>",
